Dia. 02 Follow up
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black has to capture with 1 and then White descends at 2 and \cf1\b Black is dead\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par If Black plays at 3, White captures with 4. Moreover if Black plays at 4 instead of 3, White plays dansu with 3 and Black can't live anymore.
\par }
