Dia. 03 Vital Point for Living
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par If White can't see how to capture Black, he takes at 1.
\par After that Black lives with 2.
\par If White plays at A instead of 1, Black still lives with 2.
\par This was the \cf1\b vital point for living\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par }
